Package: remoteoutcome
Type: Package
Title: Program Evaluation with Remotely Sensed Variables
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ashesh", "Rambachan", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "asheshr@stanford.edu"),
    person("Rahul", "Singh", role = "aut"),
    person("Davide", "Viviano", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides tools for estimating treatment effects using remotely 
    sensed variables (RSVs) such as satellite images or mobile phone data. 
    Implements the nonparametric methods developed in Rambachan, A., 
    Singh, R., and Viviano, D. (2025) "Program Evaluation with Remotely 
    Sensed Outcomes" <arXiv:2411.10959>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
